      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chicken fajita mix</strong> and cook for 12-15 min or until the veg has softened and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
