    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es] </strong>and <strong>remaining diced onion</strong> together as finely as you can</p>",
