    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped tomato </strong>and<strong> onion</strong> to a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
